Breif about the project:
THE PIR (Motion sensor) and LED is connected to the ESP32, when the motion sensor detects motion the LED wil turn on and vise versa

Connection:
PIR: 
    VCC: connected to the 3V3 pin in the ESP32
    Signal pin: connected to pin 22 in the ESP32
    GND: connected to GND in the ESP32

LED:
    Anode: connected to pin 23 in the ESP32
    Cathode: connected to GND in the ESP32

